'''鯽屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'' Carassius ''}}）是[[鯉科|鯉科]][[鲤亚科|鲤亚科]]下的一個屬，[[鯽魚|鯽魚]]就是其下的一個种。它們廣泛分佈于歐亞大陸，與[[鯉屬|鯉屬]]的魚類並沒有太大的親緣關係。<ref>de Graaf, Martin; Megens, Hendrik-Jan; Samallo, Johannis & Sibbing, Ferdinand A. (2007): Evolutionary origin of Lake Tana's (Ethiopia) small ''Barbus'' species: indications of rapid ecological divergence and speciation. ''[[Animal_Biology_(journal)|Anim. Biol.]]'' '''57'''(1): 39-48. {{doi|10.1163/157075607780002069}} (HTML abstract)</ref>

